    </content>
    <content lang="en">
      <city>Bern</city>
      <title>SERI News, September 16</title>
      <lead>Information from the State Secretariat for Education, Research and Innovation SERI: Apprenticeship Toolbox / A Swiss Pier in San Francisco / ESA Business Incubation Centre / ...</lead>
      <text link="no">&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Switzerland’s participation in Erasmus+&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Existing interim solution extended until the end of 2017&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A knowledge transfer project launched by the European Alliance for Apprenticeships&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The Apprenticeship Toolbox facilitates comparison of dual-track VET systems&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;General education in VET programmes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Core curriculum for general education to be implemented more consistently&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Two-year VET programmes leading to a Federal VET Certificate&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;New analyses of Federal VET Certificate programmes paint a positive picture&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ERI Network promotes the exchange of experiences and ideas&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We live in an ageing society – what can Switzerland learn from other countries?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;New centre for innovation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;A Swiss pier in San Francisco&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Swiss Innovation Park – Zurich/Dübendorf site&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Federal Council defines maximum area for Innovation Park&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Opening of the ESA Business Incubation Centre&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;New funding programme to serve as launch pad to space start-ups in Switzerland&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</text>
      <contact>info@sbfi.admin.ch</contact>
      <link id="159141">
        <title>SERI News, September 16</title>
        <uri>https://www.sbfi.admin.ch/dam/sbfi/en/dokumente/2016/09/sept-sbfi-news.pdf.download.pdf/7_16_SBFI-NEWS_en.pdf</uri>
        <position>Context</position>
      </link>
